metadata.name: #10 Stealth
metadata.description:
During the last of my fox watching sessions the three siblings were venturing farther and farther from the den and would only play around the den site for 30 minutes to an hour before going off in search of food. The bracken and ferns had grown at the site now so I had to lie down in tick infested grass to get this shot. During my fox shoots I must have removed around 8 ticks on different occasions !. I will return to the site again soon.

Stealth by Lee Pengelly 
Edition: 1/1 
Location: Devon, UK
